newpath
0 0 0 moveto3d
P aload pop rlineto3d
Q aload pop rlineto3d
Q aload pop lineto3d
closepath
gsave
0.8 setgray
fill
grestore
stroke
grestore

gsave
newpath
P 1 get P 0 get atan /T exch def 
/r P 1 get dup mul P 0 get dup mul add sqrt def
[0 0 1] T rotate3d
newpath
r 0.032 plainarrow3d
gsave
1 0 0 setrgbcolor
fill
grestore
currentlinewidth 2 div setlinewidth
stroke
grestore

